Description: Smart Claude Max account rotation
 cmaxctl routes claude invocations across multiple Claude Max accounts so
 you never hit the per-account 5-hour or 7-day cap. It uses Anthropic's
 own /api/oauth/usage endpoint as ground truth and falls back to local
 heuristics when the endpoint is unreachable.
 .
 Built on top of caam for per-account isolation. No background daemons;
 runs as a systemd-user interval timer (or crontab fallback).
